en_762089_0	A presentation on the operation ‘Barbarossa’ during the Quarter Master Officers Course 19 at Combat Training School (CTS), Ampara educated Officers and Other Ranks on Wednesday (6).
en_762089_1	The presentations were aimed at refreshing historical memories of the Operation ‘Barbarossa’.
en_762089_2	On this Occasion Brigadier P.A.D. Kahapola, Commandant, CTS, Ampara, Chief instructor, all Officers and Other Ranks attended the sessions and witnessed the presentation.
en_762089_3	Towards the end of the programme, an interactive question and answer session got underway, aimed at further enhancing their knowledge on the subject.
